            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-12-31T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="404" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d404">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>With the transmission of the report of the Western occupation authorities to
                    Paris, the negotiations for an agreement on access and communications with
                    Berlin passed to the Sixth Session of the Council <pb facs="0859" n="818" xml:id="pg_818"/> of Foreign Ministers. For documentation relating to these
                    negotiations, see <ref target="#pg_913">pages 913</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
